text: Ashinsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnovoskhodsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 121 as of 2010. There are 3 streets.Карта Иглинского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 52 km from Iglino, 9 km from Krasny Voskhod. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Ashinsky (rural locality)
